# Events App

## Architecture
MVVM + Repository + Hilt

## Features
- Offline caching (Room)
- API integration (Retrofit)
- Image caching (Glide)
- Background sync (WorkManager)

## Cache Strategy
TTL = 10 minutes

## Run Steps
1. Open in Android Studio
2. Sync Gradle
3. Run app

## Trade-offs
- Used simple TTL instead of complex cache invalidation
- Minimal UI for time constraint